OL,5, More than 200,000 children are         
OL,6, estimated to have suffered sexual abuse
OL,7, from Spain's Catholic clergy, an       
OL,8, independent commission has found.      
OL,10,FThe details emerged from an            
OL,11,Funprecedented public investigation by  
OL,12,FSpain's ombudsman, who spoke of the    
OL,13,F"devastating impact" on victims.       
OL,15,FAngel Gabilondo also criticised the    
OL,16,FChurch for its inaction and attempts to
OL,17,Fcover up or deny the abuse.            
OL,19,F"What has happened has been possible   
OL,20,Fbecause of that silence," he said.     
